{"tid":422940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女最後走咗返去搵佢男朋友","createTime":"2017-10-03T13:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T00:34:33.000Z","uid":10607,"like":4,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"952e2ed135c5a08ae59a57da11e96e6dba3d268c","tid":422940,"uid":10607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"佢嗰陣同佢BF關係唔係咁好<br />\n跟住佢黎搵我 因為我都對佢有意思<br />\n所以就同佢傾咗落去 越傾就越曖昧 佢都話想同我一齊<br />\n去到最近就約咗佢出街啦 咁就俾佢條仔發現咗<br />\n跟住佢哋就攤牌啦 <br />\n最後唔知點解就叫我以後唔好再搵佢 話佢放唔低條仔<br />\n但我已經深深愛上咗佢 我唔想冇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcad9f3081aac66ceb2b2c28ddd502dd9c486cd","tid":422940,"uid":105833,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"4f4586f34e626ef06c3c36a1ce2f5ad9e87d6b9a","tid":422940,"uid":10607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兵</blockquote><br />\n嗚嗚 點解會咁㗎<br />\n真係好鍾意佢"},{"pid":"c86a0084bcb88c4cf6d8ae2508529c74224dede7","tid":422940,"uid":127272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8d0495058c28ef6b3033ff2db48a7b01b7fe78","tid":422940,"uid":10607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a78bf0dd07d954170ba291ee6c27b0ee8b23f985","tid":422940,"uid":16880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"過眼雲煙 愛乜鬼丫 人地當你水泡咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b82bbf75c58175e3da6bccbaec460d943c7028","tid":422940,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兵</blockquote><br />\n嗚嗚 點解會咁㗎<br />\n真係好鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n愛情沒有得勉強"},{"pid":"398e77ef8369282a37f40e56c909a7a9d00296cf","tid":422940,"uid":10607,"like":0,"dislike"